'From Pharo13.1.0SNAPSHOT of 15 June 2026 [Build information: Pharo-13.1.0+SNAPSHOT.build.734.sha.45e803df96aa5e64d0ba54450f49a879af08f6ac (64 Bit)] on 8 July 2026 at 2:51:25.037619 pm'!CMAgent subclass: #AHCattleBatch	instanceVariableNames: 'heads corporalCondition dailyForrageNeed faeces owner corporalConditionDecreaseRate MinDailyForrageNeed'	classVariableNames: ''	package: 'AgriHerders-Model'!!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.744227+02:00'!corporalCondition: anObject	corporalCondition := anObject! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.744458+02:00'!corporalConditionDecreaseRate: anObject	corporalConditionDecreaseRate := anObject! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.744679+02:00'!dailyForrageNeed: anObject	dailyForrageNeed := anObject! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.747848+02:00'!faeces: anObject	faeces := anObject! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.74824+02:00'!heads: anObject	heads := anObject! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.750817+02:00'!owner	^ owner! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.751416+02:00'!owner: anObject	owner := anObject! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.745603+02:00'!defecateOn: visitedPlots	"On répartit le nombre de fècès total sur tous les plots visités. 	Ainsi, on note une Mise à jour de la fertilité des plots visités par les animaux. Excreta deposits are proportional to the time spent by the animals on the plot. ""2.8 * 4 * 183 /1000 = 2T/ha ce qui correspiond à une élévation de 1 de la fertilité (Une publication technique mentionne que pour nourrir des microorganismes du sol et améliorer certains aspects de fertilité, des apports de 2 à 4 t/ha de compost jeune de fumier peuvent déjà avoir un effet mesurable. D’où je garde 4 dans ce calcul « ""2.8 * 4 * 183 /1000 = 2T/ha ») .""le troupeau prélève 6.25 * le nombre de tête de la biomasse du couvert. Si il n’est pas rassasié et qu’il y a de plot ouvert où il peut manger, il va sur ces plots."	| qtyFaecesOnPlot |	visitedPlots ifEmpty: [ ^ self ].	qtyFaecesOnPlot := faeces * heads * (183 / visitedPlots size)	                   * (corporalCondition / 10) / 1000.	visitedPlots do: [ :plot |			plot soilFertility:				(plot soilFertility + (qtyFaecesOnPlot / 2) "min: 20") ]! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.747567+02:00'!eatForNeeds: needs	"le troupeau prélève 6.25 * le nombre de têtes de la biomasse du couvert. Retourne les besoins restants pour arriver à la sassiété"	| newNeeds |	self cell cover biomass = 0 ifTrue: [			self updateCorporalConditionWith: needs.			^ needs ].	self cell cover biomass >= needs		ifTrue: [				self cell cover biomass: self cell cover biomass - needs.				self corporalCondition: 10.				^ 0 ]		ifFalse: [				newNeeds := needs - self cell cover biomass.				self cell cover biomass: 0.				self updateCorporalConditionWith: newNeeds.				^ newNeeds ]! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.748016+02:00'!goHome self moveTo: (self owner house )! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.750078+02:00'!moveTo: aPlot"(aPlot hasOccupantsOfClass: AHCattleBatch) ifTrue: [ self halt ]."	super moveTo: aPlot.	self cell cowsCounter: self cell cowsCounter + self heads! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.75064+02:00'!naturalMortality	"Les animaux peuvent mourir de vieillesse ou de faiblesse. Le taux de mortalité augmente si la condition corporelle moyenne annuelle est mauvaise :Taux_mortalité_base = 0,02 (2 % par an)Si Condition_moyenne_annuelle < 4 :    Taux_mortalité = 0,10 (10 %)Si Condition_moyenne_annuelle < 2 :    Taux_mortalité = 0,20 (20 %)Morts_naturelles = heads × Taux_mortalité"	| taux_mortalité |	taux_mortalité := 0.02.	(self corporalCondition between: 2 and: 4) ifTrue: [		taux_mortalité := taux_mortalité + 0.1 ].	self corporalCondition < 2 ifTrue: [		taux_mortalité := taux_mortalité + 0.2 ].	self heads: (heads - (heads * taux_mortalité)) "rounded".	self heads < 1 ifTrue: [ self delete ]! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.75249+02:00'!reproduce	"La reproduction dépend directement de l’état corporel moyen des animaux pendant la saison pluvieuse (période la plus favorable).On calcule d’abord la condition moyenne du troupeau sur toute la saison pluvieuse :AverageRainySeasonCondition = mean(DailyRainySeasonCondition)Ensuite, on applique le taux de reproduction correspondant :AverageRainySeasonCondition	Taux de reproduction	Explication:> 7 => 	25 %	Bonne santé → beaucoup de naissances5 à 7	=> 15 %	Santé moyenne ; naissances modérées3 à 5 =>	5 %	Santé fragile ; très peu de naissances< 3	0 %	Santé trop mauvaise ; pas de naissancesNaissances = heads × Taux_reproduction"	self corporalCondition > 7 ifTrue: [		^ self heads: (heads * 0.25) "rounded" + heads ].	self corporalCondition > 5 ifTrue: [		^ self heads: (heads * 0.15) "rounded" + heads ].	self corporalCondition > 3 ifTrue: [		^ self heads: (heads * 0.05) "rounded" + heads ]! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.753937+02:00'!splitInTwo	"Si la taille du troupeau est > 30, alors je crée un nouveau troupeau de la taille totale du troupeau actuel moins 30.Et j'affecte ce nouveau troupeau à mon éleveur."	| newBatch |	self heads > 50 ifFalse: [ ^ nil ].	newBatch := self cormasModel newEntity: self class.	newBatch heads: self heads - 50.	self heads: 30.	newBatch owner: self owner.	owner herd add: newBatch.	newBatch goHome! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.754137+02:00'!totalNeeds"Ex : heads = 10 => 10 * 6.25 * 183 = 11437 kg/semestre.dailyForrageNeed := 6.25 kgMS, 183 jours dans un semestre"	^ self heads * self dailyForrageNeed * 183 ! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'control' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.754454+02:00'!updateCorporalConditionWith: needs	needs > 0		ifTrue: [			self corporalCondition: 10 * (1 - (needs / self totalNeeds)) ]		ifFalse: [ "Ratio = Daily-ing / dailyForrageNeeds"			self corporalCondition: 10 ]! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'controlling' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.74599+02:00'!delete self owner ifNotNil: [ owner herd remove: self ifAbsent: [nil] ].super delete.! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: '2026-07-06T17:11:22.4634+02:00'!initialize	super initialize.	"heads := 10. ""self randomIntegerBetween: 1 and: 5.""	corporalCondition := 10.	dailyForrageNeed := 6.25. 	faeces := 2.8. 	corporalConditionDecreaseRate := 0.	MinDailyForrageNeed := 4.25 "! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'pov' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.751636+02:00'!pov	<pov>	^ CMPointOfView		  color: self owner color		  shape: #star		  size: heads / 70! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'pov' stamp: '2026-07-06T13:58:12.751929+02:00'!povNumberOfHeads	<pov>	^ CMPointOfView color: (self			   colorAttribute: #heads			   min: 1			   max: 15			   color: Color red)! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing parameters' stamp: '2026-07-06T17:04:15.894988+02:00'!heads	<parameterIntegerDefault: 10>	^ heads! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing parameters' stamp: '2026-07-06T17:05:05.88095+02:00'!corporalCondition	<parameterIntegerDefault: 10>	^ corporalCondition! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing parameters' stamp: '2026-07-06T17:06:11.272928+02:00'!dailyForrageNeed"6.25 kgMS"	<parameterFloatDefault: 6.25>	^ dailyForrageNeed! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing parameters' stamp: '2026-07-06T17:09:03.858014+02:00'!corporalConditionDecreaseRate	<parameterFloatDefault: 0>	^ corporalConditionDecreaseRate! !!AHCattleBatch methodsFor: 'accessing parameters' stamp: '2026-07-06T17:08:29.502768+02:00'!faeces"2.8. kg/day"	<parameterFloatDefault: 2.8>	^ faeces! !